    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"extreme nationalism\" is a bit of a buzzword though. isnt almost any strong sense of national identity seen as \"extreme\" by people who want globalism? like, can you even have a functioning society without some level of nationalism, or is it fundamentally just a stepping stone to something worse?",
